75
00:08:14,675 --> 00:08:16,410
Boleh tolong ambilkan aiskrim
dan ikan bilis?

76
00:08:18,645 --> 00:08:21,014
Janganlah ikut nafsu
mengidam sangat.

77
00:08:21,081 --> 00:08:23,250
Tak baik untuk
kandungan.

78
00:08:23,317 --> 00:08:25,352
Kamu perlu makan banyak
labah-labah,

79
