92
00:08:59,853 --> 00:09:01,988
Terima kasih, ayah.

93
00:09:02,055 --> 00:09:06,792
Kegemaran saya ketika
saya kecil dulu.

94
00:09:17,037 --> 00:09:18,038
Maaf.

95
00:09:21,238 --> 00:09:23,238
<i>*Bersabarlah Budak*</i>

96
00:09:29,238 --> 00:09:31,438
<i>*Bilik Bersalin*</i>

97
00:09:33,153 --> 00:09:36,023
