darah dia?

216
00:16:11,151 --> 00:16:12,485
Tak.

217
00:16:12,552 --> 00:16:13,820
Sepatutnya kamu
kena minum.

218
00:16:13,887 --> 00:16:15,355
Hey! Nak buat
sesuatu yang hebat?

